HEADWORD: Synchronistic
<hw>Syn`chro*nis"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to synchronism; arranged according to correspondence in time;
<as>as, <ex>synchronistic</ex> tables</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

